Package gov.nih.nlm.ling.sem

Class Interval

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nih.nlm.ling.sem.Interval
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Interval>
    public class Interval
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Interval>
    Represents an interval with two real-valued endpoints.

    This class is intended to be used for scalar modality value operations.

    Author:
    Halil Kilicoglu
